    "text_6": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Even their kookaburra logo has a story, borrowed from Jack's grandfather's WWII regiment, and now passed down as the family emblem. \u201cIt's personal. It means something,\u201d Jack said.</p><p>And that's really what Walker Golf is all about: doing something you love, with the people you love, and doing it well.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
